<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TT2.9">
<l>kaṭuva ṉukaḷuṅ kaḻaicūḻ potumpiṟ kaḻukum pēyumā</l>
<l>yiṭuveṇ ṭalaiyu mīmap pukaiyu meḻunta peruṅkāṭṭiṟ</l>
<l>koṭuveṇ maḻuvum piṟaiyun tatumpak koḷḷeṉ ṟicaipāṭap</l>
<l>paṭuveṇ ṭuṭiyum paṟaiyuṅ kaṟaṅkap parama ṉāṭumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In the big cremation ground where white skulls that are put and smoke from the pyres rise,</l>
<l>there being vultures and demonesses in the grove surrounded by bamboo where monkeys jump,</l>
<l>while [his] curved white axe and the crescent moon swing, while [they] sing noisily,</l>
<l>while beaten white hour-glass drum and drum are resounding, the Highest one is dancing.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
